nd pleasant to everyone."},{"version":"diamond","text":"This kindhearted Pok\u00e9mon nurses sick Pok\u00e9mon to health. It senses feelings of sadness."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It is a Pok\u00e9mon that delivers happiness. Eating its egg is said to make one kind to everyone."},{"version":"platinum","text":"The eggs it lays are filled with happiness. Eating even one bite will bring a smile to anyone."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Anyone who takes even one taste of BLISSEY\u2019s egg becomes unfailingly caring and pleasant to everyone."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It has a very compassionate nature. If it sees a sick Pok\u00e9mon, it will nurse the sufferer back to health."},{"version":"black","text":"The eggs it lays are filled with happiness. Eating even one bite will bring a smile to anyone."},{"version":"white","text":"The eggs it lays are filled with happiness. Eating even one bite will bring a smile to anyone."},{"version":"black-2","text":"The eggs it lays are filled with happiness. Eating even one bite will bring a smile to anyone."},{"version":"white-2","text":"The eggs it lays are filled with happiness. Eating even one bite will bring a smile to anyone."},{"version":"x","text":"The eggs it lays are filled with happiness. Eating even one bite will bring a smile to anyone."},{"version":"y","text":"This kindhearted Pok\u00e9mon nurses sick Pok\u00e9mon to health. It senses feelings of sadness."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Blissey senses sadness with its fluffy coat of fur. If it does so, this Pok\u00e9mon will rush over to a sad person, no matter how far away, to share a Lucky Egg that brings a smile to any face."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Blissey senses sadness with its fluffy coat of fur. If it does so, this Pok\u00e9mon will rush over to a sad person, no matter how far away, to share a Lucky Egg that brings a smile to any face."},{"version":"sun","text":"Even the most ferocious Pok\u00e9mon become calm when they eat Blissey\u2019s egg, which is said to be filled with happiness."},{"version":"moon","text":"Its fluffy fur coat acts as a sensor, enabling it to read the feelings of people and Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Their eggs are such a delicacy that some say eating one will bring you happiness. These eggs fetch the highest prices on the market."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon is overflowing with love. Only Chansey that share a strong bond with their Trainer can evolve, so people say."},{"version":"sword","text":"Whenever a Blissey finds a weakened Pok\u00e9mon, it will share its egg and offer its care until the other Pok\u00e9mon is all better."},{"version":"shield","text":"Blissey lays mysterious eggs that are filled with happiness. It\u2019s said that anyone who eats a Blissey egg will start acting kindly to all others."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"A kindhearted Pok\u00e9mon that will care for any sick person or Pok\u00e9mon until their health improves. The eggs it lays are delicious and bring good fortune to those who eat them."}],"evo":{"name":"happiny","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"chansey","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":"oval-stone","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"day","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"blissey","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":160,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https